put these together there are three of what they call Positive Illusions - where people

9
00:00:44,140 --> 00:00:47,790
generally overestimate the positivity of their lives.

10
00:00:47,790 --> 00:00:52,730
So the first one is simply rating your abilities and your successes as higher than they really

11
00:00:52,730 --> 00:00:53,730
are.

12
00:00:53,730 --> 00:00:57,520
