15
00:01:03,070 --> 00:01:08,280
The second positive illusion is that we overestimate how much control we have over life.

16
00:01:08,280 --> 00:01:13,009
People tend to think they can steer their fate and produce the results that they want.

17
00:01:13,009 --> 00:01:14,219
They can get where they want to go.

18
00:01:14,219 --> 00:01:15,469
They can take charge.

19
00:01:15,469 --> 00:01:20,090
So, when people estimate how much they are in control of their own fates, people overestimate

20
00:01:20,090 --> 00:01:22,159
how much control they have.

21
00:01:22,159 --> 00:01:27,079
This is borne out even in very carefully controlled laboratory studies - where you can make the

22
