they thought, how can we change their thinking style, these people are twisting everything

30
00:01:58,170 --> 00:02:01,280
into a negative frame, how can we get them to stop doing that.

31
00:02:01,280 --> 00:02:06,270
If we could only get them to see the world more accurately, they would stop being depressed.

32
00:02:06,270 --> 00:02:10,929
