twisting things.

35
00:02:16,629 --> 00:02:18,290
But in a positive way.

36
00:02:18,290 --> 00:02:21,450
The third positive illusion is optimism.

37
00:02:21,450 --> 00:02:23,680
People are unrealistically optimistic.

38
00:02:23,680 --> 00:02:27,000
They think good things are more likely to happen to them than to the average person,

39
00:02:27,000 --> 00:02:28,819
